
下面介绍使用第三方源，安装SMPlayer

1，安装第三方源：rpmforge-release-0.5.3-1.el6.rf.x86_64.rpm
wget http://pkgs.repoforge.org/rpmforge-release/rpmforge-release-0.5.3-1.el6.rf.x86_64.rpm
rpm -ivh rpmforge-release-0.5.3-1.el6.rf.x86_64.rpm
（挂载NTFS分区也是需要这个源的：yum install fuse-ntfs-3g 或 yum install ntfs-3g ）  

2, yum install mplayer smplayer